title: Enjoy On-Site Laundry and Resident Business Center!
posting_body: ['Escape from the city and enter the gated community of Mediterranean Village with the refreshing sounds of waterfalls and fountains with a bridge over a Koi pond to welcome you home each day.', 'Lounge around our year-round resort style heated pool and take in the tropical landscapes and tranquil fountains.', 'Get your workout in our newly renovated 24 hour gym.', "Then step out to LA's exciting Sunset Blvd just footsteps away!", '- Courtyard setting with tropical landscape, fountains, and koi pond', '- Heated resort-style pool', '- 24-Hour fitness center', '- 24-Hour laundry centers', '- Elevator access', '- Gas included', '- Cable and high-speed internet available', '- Walking distance to Melrose Avenue shopping district', '- Walking distance to the Beverly Center', '- Walking distance to Santa Monica and Sunset Boulevard’s dining and grocery shopping', '- 2 miles from The Grove and The Farmers Market', '- Steps to public transportation', '- Conveniently located to the 405, 10, and 101 freeways', '- Gated property access', '- Assigned covered parking', '- On-site management available 7 days a week', '- 24-Hour emergency on-call maintenance', '- Nightly courtesy patrol', '- Full stainless-steel appliance package with gas range', '- Air conditioning', '- Studio, one-, and two-bedroom homes', '- Granite countertops', '- Mirrored closets', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*On select units and new move-ins only.', 'Pricing is subject to change.', 'Restrictions apply.', 'Call for details.']
